scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: The ISDA Master Agreement Schedule begins at line 10 with the heading 'SCHEDULE' and continues through all the 'Parts' and 'Other Provisions' that are standard for a Schedule, ending at line 352 just before the annexures (which are confirmations and notices, not part of the Schedule). The preceding lines (0-9) are cover, parties, and contact info, and lines after 352 are annexures and not part of the Schedule.
